item.title: Vulnversity
item.description: Vulnversity Vulnversity is the first room in the Offensive Security path on TryHackMe. Below is my walkthrough for the tasks for this room. Task 1 Hints Have you deployed the machine and clicked on complete? Task 2 Hints The list of flags at the beginning of this task will be of great help. Have you read the man page for nmap to answer some of these questions? Task 3 Hints Have you installed gobuster?
